Download the world's leading pregnancy tracker app today, for free week-by-week pregnancy information and articles!

The Pregnancy+ app features expert advice, daily articles, healthcare tips and interactive 3D models so you can track your baby's development. Our pregnancy app has been downloaded over 80 million times by expecting families. Join our worldwide community today! 

Baby Development
► Unique, interactive 3D models showing your baby's development 
► Baby Size Guide helps you visualise your baby's size in fruits, animals & sweets
► Pregnancy Week-by-Week Guides explain what to expect in each pregnancy week
► Simple & informative Pregnancy Timeline highlighting important milestones

Pregnancy Guides & Information
► In-depth Pregnancy Guides covering breastfeeding, exercise, food, twins & more 
► Daily Pregnancy Articles, tailored to your pregnancy stage
► 2D & 3D Scans by pregnancy week for you to browse
► Daily Blog Posts with tips, tricks & helpful advice
► Upload photos in My Bump to create a visual pregnancy diary

Pregnancy Tools
► Pregnancy Due Date Calculator helps you work out when your bundle will arrive
► Kick Counter tracks your baby's movements & activity
► Pregnancy Weight Log helps you keep an eye on changes in your weight
► Contraction Timer measures contractions throughout your labour

Organise & Plan
► Pregnancy Calendar enables you to plan & document your prenatal appointments
► Hospital Bag helps you prepare your hospital visit, for Mother, Birth Partner & Baby
► Birth Plan allows you to customise, organise & export your needs & wishes
► To-Do List & Baby Shopping List for ideas of what you need to do & buy
► Search thousands of Baby Names for inspiration & share your favourites

Our EXCLUSIVE 3D Models
Enjoy our unique 3D models showing your pregnancy's week-by-week development, from blastocyst to foetus to baby. Our 3D models truly help you to connect with the baby growing inside you. 
► Choose from multiple ethnicities
► Zoom in or out & rotate to see the baby's intricate detail
► Watch guided pregnancy week-by-week walk-throughs
► Tap to see baby movements

Pregnancy Articles & Guides
If you're feeling overwhelmed by all the advice out there, don't worry. Our Pregnancy + tracker app will guide you through your pregnancy, week-by-week, keeping you up to date with your baby's development and helping you stay healthy through pregnancy and beyond. The Pregnancy+ app content is written in-house, with the help of medical experts, lactation consultants, midwives and, of course, parents.

Share your journey with friends & family
Our pregnancy tracker app can be personalised so your partner, future grandparents or best friend can join in the fun and follow your baby's development in the womb, from bump to birth! Keep everyone up to date with your pregnancy by inviting them to download the app today.

Discover the BabyCentre Pregnancy Tracker and Baby App – your perfect companion for pregnancy and parenthood!
Expecting? BabyCentre’s Pregnancy Tracker app is here to guide you every step of the way! Track your pregnancy week by week and day by day with expert pregnancy tips, foetal development videos, and content tailored to your unique pregnancy and parenting journey. Just enter your baby’s due date, and let our pregnancy app bring you personalised guidance, advice, and tools from the start of your pregnancy right through to your baby’s first birthday.
Our BabyCentre Pregnancy and Baby app offers everything you need in one place:
Track your journey with our pregnancy tracker
	•	Get daily updates on how your baby is developing, tailored to your exact stage of pregnancy.
	•	Enjoy a daily news feed with tips on pregnancy nutrition, pregnancy exercise, and pregnancy symptom management.
	•	Weekly pregnancy reminders, pregnancy checklists, and pregnancy insights make staying informed easy and fun!
Instant expert advice for pregnancy at your fingertips
	•	Need answers to your pregnancy questions? Our team of Midwives is here to help with real-time support for any pregnancy questions that come up.
	•	Access hundreds of expert articles on every pregnancy topic from BabyCentre, guiding you from bump to baby.
Join a community of mums and new parents
	•	Connect with mums-to-be in your Birth Club, where you can share, ask, and learn about pregnancy together.
	•	Chat with other parents about baby names, early pregnancy symptoms, baby essentials, and everything else related to pregnancy.
Find the perfect baby name
	•	Looking for a baby name finder? Our Baby Name Tool helps you explore thousands of baby names and meanings for your pregnancy journey.
…and so much more!
	•	Use our due date calculator to track your pregnancy, see interactive foetal development images throughout pregnancy, track your bump in our “Bumpie” pregnancy photo diary, and dive into exclusive “Inside the Uterus” pregnancy videos.
From pregnancy to the first year of your baby’s life, our pregnancy app evolves with you, bringing expert pregnancy advice, a supportive community, and all the essential tools you need for a smooth pregnancy experience.
Download the BabyCentre Pregnancy and Baby App today and enjoy every step of your pregnancy journey!
All health information in our pregnancy app is approved by the BabyCentre Medical Advisory Board and certified by the NHS England Information Standard.

*** Most downloaded Contraction Timer app in the world! Number 1 in the UK, USA, Australia, Canada, Italy and elsewhere! ***

This is the simplest-to-use contraction timer. The app will help to track your contractions and determine when it's time to go to the hospital.
If you plan on having a home birth, the app will tell you what stage of labor you are in at any given moment.

Keep track of your labor by tapping a single button at the start and at the end of each contraction. The Contraction Timer analyzes the duration and frequency of contractions and will notify you when it's time to go to the hospital.

Thousands of pregnant women around the world have become mothers using our app.

Always consult your doctor to orient yourself in terms of contraction frequency and duration.
This app is not a medical device and our recomendations are based on standard indicators. Your labor may occur differently. Therefore, do not rely exclusively on our app.
If the duration and frequency of contractions do not yet correspond to the necessary indicators but labor pains become unbearable, it is better to go to the hospital as soon as possible rather than give birth at home or on the way there. Trust what your body is telling you.

If you have any questions or suggestions, please email us at neumandev@gmail.com. Your feedback is very important to us.

Estimate your body temperature, log and track your data, making it easier to spot potential fever symptoms—all without a thermometer!

Knowing your temperature is crucial for maintaining well-being and taking the best care of yourself, so stay proactive about your health by monitoring your body temperature with our app. With just a few simple steps on your mobile device,  you can track your body temperature trends and take proactive steps towards your health goals.


But wait – there's more: 

• Find out, track and log your body temperature with ease.

• Log and easily export your body temperature data and more into PDF to share with your doctor.

• Easily measure wrist temperature with the Apple Watch app and save your data in our app. (requires Apple Watch 8 or newer)

• Use your phone’s camera to estimate your heart rate and then easily log your data afterward.

• Track, log, and export your symptoms and medications effortlessly.

• Monitor the heat index based on location to safeguard yourself against heat-related conditions that could pose health risks.

• Add family members and monitor the body temperature of each.

• Discover how weather conditions can influence your body temperature using our widget.


Whether you're at home or on the go, managing your health has never been easier.

The Body Temperature App for Fever is free to download and utilize. However, users can opt for a subscription to access additional features. Your subscription will automatically renew and you’ll be billed based on the plan you choose. You can cancel your subscription at any time in the App Store.

Disclaimer: For wellness use only. The App is intended to improve your awareness of general wellness. The App can't be used for diagnostics or medical purposes. The App does not diagnose, treat, mitigate or prevent any disease, symptom, disorder or abnormal physical state. Always seek a health care professional or emergency services if you believe you may have a medical issue.

Save your precious time with the fastest gestational age calculator.

It will provide you valuable information such as estimated date of delivery based on last menstrual period (LMP) or based on ultrasound.

The app features a practical and intuitive gestational BMI calculator, essential for the weight management of the pregnant women. BMI recommendation changes as the gestational age increases.

On top of that, there's an estimate of the fetal weight for the given gestational age, based on Hadlock study. You can intuitively track the progress of the pregnancy.

We know that as a healthcare professional you should not waste time with awkward apps. Try for yourself and see how fast you can get the information you need.

You can also easily choose dark or light theme.

O Contador de Contrações gratuito é a ferramenta perfeita para você controlar suas contrações e saber se você deveria ir para o hospital - ou se está cedo!



- Cronometre contrações e intervalos
- Entenda a frequência e durações médias
- Compartilhe ao vivo com sua equipe médica


Não é preciso fazer nenhum tipo de cadastro, e a ferramenta não possui anúncios. Ao abrir o app, basta apertar "Play" na sua primeira contração e o cronômetro começará a contar.


É possível compartilhar o Resumo das contrações (durante ou ao final), ou transmitir ao vivo para sua equipe médica - assim, todo mundo pode acompanhar suas contrações e intervalos em tempo real.


O compartilhamento ocorre através de um link único, e totalmente confidencial.


Este aplicativo foi feito e é mantido pela equipe do Nattal - Cartão de pré-natal digital.

تطبيق دبي الصحية الجديد هو منصة ذكية شاملة توفر لكم جميع الخدمات الطبية المتوفرة في المنشآت التابعة لدبي الصحية، فمن خلاله تستطيعون الوصول للكثير من الخدمات المتنوعة بطريقة سهلة وسلسة.
تشمل هذه الخدمات: حجز المواعيد وإدارتها، الحصول على النتائج المخبرية ووصفات الأدوية، التأكد من حالة طلب فحص اللياقة الطبية، التسجيل والتطوع لخدمات التبرع بالدم، كل هذا وأكثر متوفر باللغتين العربية والانجليزية.




الخدمات المتوفرة على التطبيق: 
•	الاطلاع على السجلات الطبية – النتائج المخبرية، وصفات الأدوية
•	حجز، وإدارة، وإلغاء المواعيد الخاصة بالمنشآت الطبية التابعة لدبي الصحية
•	متابعة آنية لحالة طلب فحص اللياقة الطبية
•	تحميل شهادة الإجازة المرضية المصدقة  
•	التسجيل للتبرع بالدم، والحصول على كافة المعلومات عن خدمات التبرع بالدم
•	خريطة تفاعلية تساعد على البحث وتحديد أقرب المستشفيات، ومراكز الرعاية الأولية، والتخصصات الطبية ومراكز اللياقة الطبية التابعة لدبي الصحية
•	طرق متنوعة لتسجيل الدخول: باستخدام رقم البطاقة الصحية الصادرة من دبي الصحية MRN، أو باستخدام الهوية الرقمية الإماراتية، إضافة إلى إمكانية استخدام بصمة الإصبع أو خاصية التعرف على الوجه.
•	استلام الإشعارات والتذكيرات
•	إضافة حسابات أفراد العائلة لإدارة ملفاتهم الطبية
•	ترتيب الشاشة الرئيسية لكل أفراد العائلة لتجربة مشخصنة
•	تحميل وتتبع بيانات الصحة واللياقة البدنية، بما في ذلك عند التسجيل في ،'Apple Health' البيانات من تطبيق برامج التتبع الذاتي.



ترقّبوا المزيد، نعمل بشكل دوري على تحسين تجربتكم وإضافة تشكيلة خدمات جديدة تلبي كافة احتياجاتكم

From the National Kidney Foundation (NKF), this application allows medical professionals to estimate kidney function using five separate eGFR calculators:

- CKD-EPI Creatinine 2021 Equation (Preferred method)
- Revised Bedside Schwartz Formula (For ages 1-17)
- Cockcroft-Gault Formula
- CKD-EPI Cystatin C 2012 Equation
- CKD-EPI Creatinine - Cystatin C 2021 Equation

Also includes information on:

-Glomerular filtration rate (GFR)
-Chronic kidney disease (CKD)
-Clinical use on how to test, evaluate, and slow progression
-Formulas

The National Kidney Foundation is the leading organization in the U.S. dedicated to the awareness, prevention, and treatment of kidney disease for hundreds of thousands of healthcare professionals, millions of patients and their families, and tens of millions of Americans at risk.
By supporting the National Kidney Foundation, you directly influence and positively impact the lives of those at risk for kidney disease, those living with chronic kidney disease, and those who care for and about them.

Experience with us the fascination of newly emerged life. Watch wonderful ultrasound videos of babies in different weeks of pregnancy. If you want, you can get to know the most important structures that can be demonstrated in ultrasound and then apply and deepen your knowledge in the ultrasound simulator. This will help you understand the growth of your own baby.

ScanBaby is divided into three different modes:

-Scan mode: Here you can scan a baby all by yourself (not your own actual baby). Turn on labelling mode to see all the important structures colored. This way you can compare the ScanBaby image to your own ultrasound image and understand the shown structures better.

-Learn mode: This beautifully crafted mode teaches you about the developmental stages of your child. Get to know all the changes that happen to you and your baby during pregnancy. We have included artfully crafted 3D scans of real babies that you can move around all by yourself and experience how your baby might currently look like. Of course all of these scans come with labelling as well.

-Watch mode: Here we have included many different ultrasound videos you might actually see in a similar way during your own examination. All come with a short explanation what can be seen. Watch a baby dance inside the uterus, play with the umbilical cord and even react to the caressing of the father.

Terms of use: https://scanbooster.com/index.php/impressum#qx-heading-1479

Please note that we have researched the information presented here with the best of our knowledge and in cooperation with medical experts, but of course we do not assume any guarantee or liability of any kind. Furthermore, the App may under no circumstances be used for medical purposes of any kind. It is intended for the sole purpose of entertainment. All of the displayed babies are already included in the app and therefore NOT your own. Furthermore ScanBaby does not transform your device into an ultrasound probe or similar, nor does it enable you to perform an ultrasound examination on yourself or anybody else. In addition to using this app and before making any medical decisions, the advice of a licensed medical doctor should always be sought.

Ele fornecerá informações valiosas, como a data estimada de parto com base no último período menstrual (DUM) ou com base no ultrassom.

O aplicativo faz uma estimativa do peso fetal para uma determinada idade gestacional, com base no estudo de Hadlock. Você pode acompanhar intuitivamente o progresso da gravidez.

Você pode também realizar a dinâmica uterina medindo com mais precisão o tempo das contrações.

Heart Rate — Your Personal Health Tracker

Your heart health is the foundation of your overall well-being, and staying on top of it is the key to a healthier, more active life. Heart Rate is a simple, intuitive, and powerful app designed to monitor your pulse, analyze health data, and support smarter lifestyle decisions.

Why Heart Rate Matters

Your pulse speaks volumes about your health. By regularly tracking it, you can detect changes early and gain a deeper understanding of your body. Whether you're managing blood pressure, aiming to lose weight, or just staying informed, Heart Rate is the perfect companion.

Features That Work for You
• Daily Pulse Measurement with the Camera. Just place your finger on the camera to get started — no special devices needed.
• Blood Pressure Tracking. Log your readings to monitor trends and spot crucial changes.
• Symptom Journal and Wellness Tracking. Record how you feel to uncover connections between symptoms and activity.
• Detailed Graphs for Any Timeframe. View your data over a day, (month and year available by subscription)  with clear, visual insights.
• Measurement History and Insights. Keep all your records in one place for easy analysis or sharing with your doctor(available by subscription).
• Apple Watch Support. Measure your pulse directly from your wrist.
• Physical Fitness Analysis. See how your endurance and activity levels are improving.
• Heart Rate Zones. Discover when you're burning fat or boosting your cardio performance.
• Apple Health Integration. All your health data synced for seamless access.
• Compare Your Data to Norms. See how your stats stack up against averages for your age and gender.
• Informative Articles and Tips. Learn about the most critical heart health metrics and how to improve them.

The Analysis Tab: Our Crown Jewel

We’re especially proud of this feature. The Analysis tab goes beyond numbers. It gives you a full picture of your heart health, comparing your resting heart rate and endurance with statistical norms for your age and gender. For fitness enthusiasts, it even identifies pulse zones to help you maximize fat burn or enhance cardio performance. Everything is straightforward, actionable, and built to make your health journey smoother.

Important Disclaimer

The Heart Rate app is for informational purposes only and is not intended for medical use. Always consult a doctor for diagnosis and treatment.

Heart Rate is your ultimate tool for health tracking, making it easier than ever to stay informed, proactive, and in control. Start prioritizing your heart today!

"Anatomy 3D Atlas" allows you to study human anatomy in an easy and interactive way. 
Through a simple and intuitive interface it is possible to observe every anatomical structure from any angle.
The anatomical 3D models are particularly detailed and with textures up to 4k resolution.

The subdivision by regions and the predefined views facilitate the observation and the study of single parts or groups of systems and the relationships between different organs.

"Anatomy - 3D Atlas" is an application aimed at medical students, doctors, physiotherapists, paramedics, nurses, athletic trainers and in anyone interested in deepening their knowledge of human anatomy.
This app is a fantastic tool to complement classic human anatomy books.

ANATOMICAL 3D MODELS
• Musculoskeletal system
• Cardiovascular system
• Nervous system
• Respiratory System
• Digestive System
• Urogenital system (male and female)
• Endocrine system
• Lymphatic system
• Eye and ear system

FEATURES
• Simple and intuitive interface
• Rotate and zoom each model in 3D space
• Option to hide or isolate single or multiple selected models
• Filter to hide or display each system
• Search function to easily find every anatomical part
• Bookmark function to save custom views
• Smart rotation which moves the center of rotation automatically
• Transparency function
• Visualization of muscles through levels of layers from the superficial ones down to the deepest ones
• By selecting a model or a pin, the related anatomical term shows up
• Description of the muscles: origin, insertion, innervation and action
• Show/Hide UI interface (very useful with small screens)

MULTILINGUAL
• The anatomical terms and the user interface are available in 12 languages: Latin, English, French, German, Italian, Portuguese, Russian, Spanish, Chinese, Japanese, Korean and Turkish
• The anatomical terms can be displayed in two languages simultaneously
